Description: Shared frontend context for all Cursor queries

Framework: Next.js (Pages Router)
Libraries: Chakra UI, Zustand, Wagmi, RainbowKit (currently), React Query, Ethers.js
Store location: src/store.ts (Zustand single global store)
Key Zustand state slices:
- User/Wallet state: userEthAddress, ethersRpcProvider, etc.
- Swap state: depositMode, selectedInputAsset, btcOutputAmount, etc.
- UI state: currencyModalTitle, deposit/withdraw modals, etc.

Project Structure:
- Pages: src/pages (index, activity, swap dynamic route, offline fallback)
- Components: src/components (by feature: swap, deposit, activity, other)
- Utilities: src/utils (colors.ts, constants.ts, helpers)
- Hooks: src/hooks (useWindowSize, custom hooks)
- Blockchain ABIs: src/abis (RiftExchange.json, etc.)
- Theme: src/theme.ts (Chakra UI customization)

Routing via Next.js Link/useRouter, global state via Zustand, blockchain via Wagmi/Ethers.
